


fog = 霧

主
The fog is very thick today.

受
I can't see anything through the fog.


The fog is very thick today.
Drive carefully in the fog.
We couldn’t see the mountains because of the fog.
The fog disappears after sunrise.
Early morning fog makes the city look mysterious.


⚠️ 小提醒
fog = 名詞
foggy = 形容詞 → 有霧的
